model.name: Bachmann2011 - Division of labor by dual feedback regulators controls JAK2/STAT5 signaling over broad ligand range

body.pre: This is a dynamic pathway model examining the roles of of the two transcriptional negative feedback regulators of the suppressor of cytokine signaling (SOCS) family, CIS and SOCS3, in JAK/STAT5 signaling, within the context of primary erythroid progenitor cells.
